{"tid":48704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隱瞞財務狀況獲批50萬貸款　男警長欺詐罪成押後判　求情指有持續還款","createTime":"2016-12-21T08:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T08:57:35.000Z","uid":37554,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"60c4d4e14d95e369ea7a1977c072bd73caf4ed13","tid":48704,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:33:27.000Z","msg":"男警長被指於2009至2013年期間，6次在向警察儲蓄互助社申請貸款時隱瞞財務狀況，獲批共50萬元貸款，裁判官認為被告有意詐騙，裁定他6項欺詐罪成。被告還押至1月10日，待索取背景報告後再判刑。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官認為，被告陳毓鈞已任職警察超過20年，必然知道借款時須準確披露自己的財務狀況，而且被告每月最低還款額已佔其收入的大部分，甚至超過每月收入，故裁判官相信被告蓄意對自己的債項不作披露，遂裁定欺詐罪名成立。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情指被告已婚，育有一個11歲的兒子，目前已經停職。被告承認其財務狀況不理想，但在向互助社借款後一直有還款，未曾拖欠還款超過3個月，互助社未有損失。裁判官押後案件至明年1月10日，待索取背景報告再判刑，其間被告不准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他報道：觀塘法院女警偷竊案開庭　官下令重新排期提早休庭：一天審唔完<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他報道：3休班警與3女街頭群毆　同涉打架被捕"},{"pid":"a15c7db9699e49fe850457f918ab4eb69804e725","tid":48704,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:38:01.000Z","msg":"quote埋其他新聞先係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc75ef6e58158b2781572971e96a46f3be63f3a","tid":48704,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:46:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>quote埋其他新聞先係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bdb9c0dee36c2ec335f6c077b7144039017f9e5","tid":48704,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:50:32.000Z","msg":"請成千警察唔討論<br />\n休班警post就一個又一個<br />\n精神自慰真係勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6bb854ffce9e9987e6f90ff8ec7a45bbcfdc322","tid":48704,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:57:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>quote埋其他新聞先係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最大犯罪集團"}]}